SystemC Installation:
---------------------

git clone https://github.com/systemc/systemc-2.3.git

cd systemc-2.3
mkdir objdir
cd objdir
export CXX=g++
../configure --prefix=/usr/local/systemc-2.3
make
sudo make install

## Set the environmental variable for SystemC installation directory
export SYSTEMC_HOME=/usr/local/systemc-2.3



## Let's first make sure your SystemC installation works fine.
## Try running the following command:

source build_hello.sh

## If the compilation was successful, Then run:

./hello


